item.dc:creator: @r0ckstar96 r0ckstar96
item.description:
@r0ckstar96 wrote:

are you connected to any other computers? Is your computer primary or secondary? I got the same problem and found out I didn’t have the router connected to my comp, but my parent’s computer did and I use their internet connection on my comp. So just download uTorrent, install, open up, go to Options>Preferences>Connection, change port to 43594, click apply, click ok and [X] out
